		(property "Description" "PYTHON 1300 / VITA 1300 1.3 MP global shutter CMOS image sensor, 10-bit parallel CMOS output, 48-pin LCC 14.22 x 14.22 mm. NOTE: pin 21 is clk_out on this variant, NOT gnd_18 as on the LVDS variant. Parallel variant is limited to 37 fps (VITA) at full resolution."
